| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2303 — Mass File Rename (alphv)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e8ee09d0-2ad3-5916-9949-aec7321543fc"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
